---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import { business } from '../data/business';
---

<Layout 
  title="Privacy Policy"
  description="Privacy policy for Sparkling Clean Oven Cleaning. How we collect, use and protect your personal information."
  canonicalUrl="/privacy/"
>
  <section class="legal-page">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="legal-content">
        <h1>Privacy Policy</h1>
        <p class="last-updated">Last updated: January 2024</p>
        
        <h2>Introduction</h2>
        <p>This privacy policy explains how {business.name} ("we", "us", "our") collects, uses, and protects your personal information when you use our website or services.</p>
        
        <h2>Information We Collect</h2>
        <p>We may collect the following information:</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Name and contact details (phone number, email address)</li>
          <li>Address and postcode</li>
          <li>Details of your appliance(s) for service quotations</li>
          <li>Correspondence and communication records</li>
        </ul>
        
        <h2>How We Use Your Information</h2>
        <p>We use your information to:</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Provide quotations for our services</li>
          <li>Schedule and deliver our oven cleaning services</li>
          <li>Communicate with you about bookings and appointments</li>
          <li>Send receipts and invoices</li>
          <li>Improve our services</li>
        </ul>
        
        <h2>Data Protection</h2>
        <p>We are committed to protecting your personal information. We implement appropriate security measures to prevent unauthorised access, disclosure, or destruction of your data.</p>
        
        <h2>Data Sharing</h2>
        <p>We do not sell, trade, or share your personal information with third parties for marketing purposes. We may share your information with:</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Service providers who assist in our operations (e.g., payment processing)</li>
          <li>Legal authorities if required by law</li>
        </ul>
        
        <h2>Your Rights</h2>
        <p>Under UK data protection law, you have the right to:</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Access the personal data we hold about you</li>
          <li>Request correction of inaccurate data</li>
          <li>Request deletion of your data</li>
          <li>Object to processing of your data</li>
          <li>Request data portability</li>
        </ul>
        
        <h2>Cookies</h2>
        <p>This website uses minimal cookies for essential functionality. We do not use tracking or advertising cookies.</p>
        
        <h2>Changes to This Policy</h2>
        <p>We may update this privacy policy from time to time. Any changes will be posted on this page with an updated revision date.</p>
        
        <h2>Contact Us</h2>
        <p>If you have any questions about this privacy policy or how we handle your personal information, please contact us:</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Phone: <a href={`tel:${business.phone}`}>{business.phoneFormatted}</a></li>
          <li>Email: <a href={`mailto:${business.email}`}>{business.email}</a></li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>

<style>
  .legal-page {
    padding: calc(var(--header-height) + var(--space-2xl)) 0 var(--space-3xl);
  }
  
  .legal-content {
    max-width: 800px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }
  
  .legal-content h1 {
    font-size: 2.5rem;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-sm);
  }
  
  .last-updated {
    color: var(--color-text-subtle);
    font-size: 0.875rem;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-2xl);
  }
  
  .legal-content h2 {
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    color: var(--color-gold);
    margin-top: var(--space-xl);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-sm);
  }
  
  .legal-content p {
    line-height: 1.7;
  }
  
  .legal-content ul {
    margin: var(--space-sm) 0 var(--space-md);
    padding-left: var(--space-lg);
  }
  
  .legal-content li {
    margin-bottom: var(--space-xs);
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
  }
</style>
